Added Configuration Space extended Version of the Traversability Map
Configuration Space extension is done automatically on adding and removal of obstacle cells. 
This is pure configuration space extension, not a riskmap biassing the robot away from obstacles what will be implemented in another subclass of TraversabilityMap


