r605 | poftwaresatent | 2007-04-28 11:00:02 -0700 (Sat, 28 Apr 2007) | 10 lines

Merged branch --ruag-demo:
* Added Mapper2d::SwipedUpdate() to remove WS obstacles when a laser
  ray traverses them.
* Extended scan_data with a boolean in_range which helps client code
  to decide if a laser point corresponds to an actual measurement.
* Added Multiscanner::CollectRawScans() which does not filter out
  readings that are out of range (useful for swiped map updates).
* Kristijan added GoalManager::ParseConfigSimple() which allows to
  parse the log replay files used on ASL's SmartTer robot.

